{"tid":506078,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毒果：燒山又中！蕭若元「燈力」驚人之樂視自盡篇","createTime":"2017-12-21T23:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T00:18:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6df941c3b81ec91db82c973a5c5c79d507587c","tid":506078,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T23:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171222/20252627?_ga=2.244985733.1861390904.1513823650-1501289292.1513130185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F20252627%3F_ga%3D2.244985733.1861390904.1513823650-1501289292.1513130185&d=oeARplCgSqAVWF6UH26Kk4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=317342c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F20252627%3F_ga%3D2.244985733.1861390904.1513823650-1501289292.1513130185&h=54debe86\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171222/20252627?_ga=2.244985733.1861390904.1513823650-1501289292.1513130185</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513850118_da07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513850118_da07.jpg&h=840b0ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂視香港自行清盤，連登網民又發現「燈神」蕭若元，原來早在2015年，已大讚樂視能於香港電視爭霸戰中突圍，紛紛高呼「蕭生好嘢」！他於片中稱「樂視具備了擊敗TVB的條件」，數十億投得英超轉播權、平價賣電視，用戶廣泛，廣告收益龐大，而且目標為重奪整個華人社會的市場，雄霸華人社會；他又認為在樂視影響下，有線和NowTV客源應下跌3、4成，TVB平均收視亦在樂視啟播後，下跌到19點左右，1年後跌至15點，5年內轉盈為虧。<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元「燈力」向來備受網民吹捧，他就港大退聯、英國脫歐、特朗普慘敗等的預測均悉數落空，今次被「考古」出樂視稱霸評論，就有網民問蕭有沒有講過股票，看來一眾財經燈神要嚴陣以待了。"},{"pid":"76fe4b08f56ec18df657681af78efd2adc87c70f","tid":506078,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T23:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" c